We want to call the function print_user_model from print_user_route from main.

Letâ€™s make the same changes as before - declaring submodules, making functions public and adding the mod.rs file.

my_project
â”œâ”€â”€ Cargo.toml
â””â”€â”¬ src
  â”œâ”€â”€ main.rs
  â”œâ”€â”€ config.rs
